Enum ProxyConfigPropertyName

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ProxyConfigPropertyName>
      • com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.app.proxy.ProxyConfigPropertyName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyName, Serializable, Comparable<ProxyConfigPropertyName>

    @Immutable
public enum ProxyConfigPropertyName
extends Enum<ProxyConfigPropertyName>
implements PropertyName
    Represents names of properties that are specified by the Proxy Config.

    Property MUST be considered mandatory unless otherwise is specified.
